            "title": "盤中速報 - 精拓科(4951)大漲7.19%，報83.5元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>精拓科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:4951:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4951\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4951-TW</a>)25日12:34股價上漲5.6元，報83.5元，漲幅7.19%，成交1,599張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>精拓科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:4951:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4951\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4951-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為電腦IC產品。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲2.64%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.78%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-126 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+104 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-230 張</li> <li>融資增減：-3 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6124760",
